<h2 class="bold font-l">Elwood and Anita's Salsa Dance</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When Owen and Paige are not gonna make it in time to show the auditor, Anita, the receipt to prove he isn't misusing funds, Anita is about to inform Mayor Whitebottom about it, which would get Owen fired. Birdie is able to stall time for Owen and Paige by playing salsa music in the background for Anita to hear so she can dance to it and Elwood offers to dance with her. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
